'''苏尔坦·本·萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特'''（{{lang-ar|سلطان بن سلمان بن عبد العزيز آل سعود}}，{{bd|1956年|6月27日|catIdx=Saud, Sultan bin Salman Al}}），退役[[沙特阿拉伯皇家空军|沙特阿拉伯皇家空军]]飛行員，為美國[[STS-51-G|STS-51-G]]的太空人之一，在太空任務中作為[[Payload_Specialist|有效載荷]]專家，為[[沙地王朝|沙烏地阿拉伯]]王室成員。他是第一位皇室成員的太空人，以及第一位[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯]]和[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]太空人。

== 早年生活 ==
Sultan1956年6月27日出生於[[利雅德|利雅德]]。<ref name=scta>{{cite web |title=Sultan bin Salman bin Abdulaziz |url=http://www.scta.gov.sa/en/AboutSCTA/HRHCV/Pages/PrinceHomePage.aspx |publisher=Saudi Commission for Tourism and Antiques |accessdate=24 May 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606133953/http://www.scta.gov.sa/en/AboutSCTA/HRHCV/Pages/PrinceHomePage.aspx |archive-date=2012-06-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=spacefacts>{{cite web |title=Biographies of international astronauts |url=http://www.spacefacts.de/bios/international/english/alsaud_salman.htm |publisher=Space Facts |accessdate=24 May 2012 |archive-date=2017-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314001750/http://www.spacefacts.de/bios/international/english/alsaud_salman.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他是[[萨勒曼·本·阿卜杜勒-阿齐兹·阿勒沙特|萨勒曼國王]]的第二個兒子。<ref name=bio>{{cite web |title=Sultan bin Salman bin Abdulaziz |url=http://www.sultanbinsalman.sa/SitePages/PrinceCVs.aspx |work=Official Website |accessdate=13 April 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130706111615/http://www.sultanbinsalman.sa/SitePages/PrinceCVs.aspx |archivedate=6 July 2013 }}</ref>他長兄Fahad出生於1955年7月20日過世於2000年。 他母親為Sultana bint Turki Al Sudairi，去世於2011年<ref>{{cite web |title=Princess Sultana bint Turki Al Sudairi dies |url=http://www.lifeinriyadh.com/princess-sultana-bint-turki-al-sudairy-dies |work=Arab News |accessdate=4 May 2012 |date=1 August 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015154950/http://www.lifeinriyadh.com/princess-sultana-bint-turki-al-sudairy-dies |archivedate=15 October 2012 }}</ref>她是薩勒曼舅父Turki bin Ahmad Al Sudairi的女兒，<ref>{{cite news |title=Sultana, wife of Riyadh Emir, passes away |url=http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentID=20110803106640 |accessdate=26 May 2012 |newspaper=Saudi Gazette |date=3 August 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228132942/http://www.saudigazette.com.sa/index.cfm?method=home.regcon&contentID=20110803106640 |archivedate=28 December 2013 }}</ref>，他是Jouf、Jizan和[[Asir_Province|Asir Province]]前政府官員並且是他的堂兄弟阿卜杜勒阿齊茲·本·沙特的創始人的統一運動的參與者。<ref name=datsultana>{{cite web |title=Sultana bint Ahmad bin Muhammad al Sudairi |url=http://www.datarabia.com/royals/viewBio.do?id=176248 |publisher=Datarabia |accessdate=8 May 2012}}</ref> and Prince Sultan is a full brother of [[Fahd_bin_Salman_bin_Abdulaziz_Al_Saud|Fahd]], [[Ahmed_bin_Salman_bin_Abdulaziz_Al_Saud|Ahmed]], [[Abdulaziz_bin_Salman|Abdulaziz]], [[Faisal_bin_Salman_bin_Abdulaziz_Al_Saud|Faisal]] and Hussa (born 1974).<ref>{{cite web |title=Family Tree of Salman bin Abdulaziz bin Abdul Rahman Al Saud |url=http://www.datarabia.com/royals/famtree.do?id=176822 |publisher=Datarabia |accessdate=1 May 2012 |archive-date=2013-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629115259/http://www.datarabia.com/royals/famtree.do?id=176822 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=siasat11>{{cite news |title=Kingdom mourns loss of princess |url=http://www.siasat.com/english/news/kingdom-mourns-loss-princess |accessdate=26 May 2012 |newspaper=The Siasat Daily |date=3 August 2011 |archive-date=2015-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705034200/http://www.siasat.com/english/news/kingdom-mourns-loss-princess |dead-url=no }}</ref>

